- Did I not tell you to shut up?

856
01:12:44,542 --> 01:12:46,458
Who are you? What's your name?

857
01:12:47,542 --> 01:12:49,167
Vijay. Vijay Chauhan.

858
01:12:50,375 --> 01:12:51,458
Vijay Chauhan?

859
