Yes, full name.

860
01:12:54,500 --> 01:12:55,625
What are you doing in my town?

861
01:12:58,792 --> 01:12:59,958
Your town?

862
01:13:01,000 --> 01:13:02,083
My car broke down.

863
01:13:05,875 --> 01:13:08,042
I'll see you in the evening?

864
01:13:09,917 --> 01:13:10,833
